OL,3,CPolice probe 'verbal threats' claim as
OL,4,CReform UK suspends MP Rupert Lowe
OL,6,FReform UK has suspended MP Rupert Lowe
OL,7,Fand reported him to the police,
OL,8,Faccusing him of threatening violence
OL,9,Ftowards the party chairman a day after
OL,10,Fhe criticised leader Nigel Farage.
OL,12,FScotland Yard said a complaint of
OL,13,F"verbal threats" made on Thursday
OL,14,Fabout an alleged incident last
OL,15,FDecember was being assessed by
OL,16,Fofficers after Mr Lowe, who was
OL,17,Felected to his Great Yarmouth seat
OL,18,Flast year, lost the whip on Friday.
