OL,6,FIn a statement, Reform said it had
OL,7,Freceived evidence of "serious
OL,8,Fbullying" and "derogatory" remarks
OL,9,Fmade about women in the MP's offices,
OL,10,Fwith two separate staffers said to
OL,11,Fhave made allegations.
OL,13,FHe was also accused of having "on at
OL,14,Fleast two occasions made threats of
OL,15,Fphysical violence" to party chairman
OL,16,FZia Yusuf, who said the matter was
OL,17,F"with the police".
