OL,6,FMr Farage said that a King's Counsel
OL,7,Fhad been appointed by the party last
OL,8,Fweek to look at the bullying
OL,9,Fcomplaints made by two separate women
OL,10,Fworking for Mr Lowe.
OL,12,FIt comes after internal splits within
OL,13,Fthe right-wing party, which has five
OL,14,FMPs, opened up on Thursday as Mr Lowe
OL,15,Ftold the Daily Mail that Reform
OL,16,Fremains a "protest party led by the
OL,17,FMessiah" under Mr Farage.
