OL,6,FAsked whether the former Ukip leader
OL,7,Fhad the potential to become prime
OL,8,Fminister, as his supporters have
OL,9,Fsuggested, Mr Lowe said: "It's too
OL,10,Fearly to know whether Nigel will
OL,11,Fdeliver the goods. He can only deliver
OL,12,Fif he surrounds himself with the right
OL,13,Fpeople."
OL,15,FOn Friday, the party claimed it had
OL,16,Freceived complaints from two women,
OL,17,Fone working in Mr Lowe's parliamentary
OL,18,Foffice and one in his constituency
OL,19,Foffice, about "serious bullying".
